Titolo: Collapse (2008 video game)

Anno: 2008

Descrizione: Collapse (Ukrainian: Kолапс, also known as Collapse: Devastated World) is an action game released in 2008 for Microsoft Windows. It was developed by Creoteam, a company based in Ukraine. The game is notable for combining Quick Time Events and sword battles similar to God of War series, third-person shooting, and a setting similar to S.T.A.L.K.E.R.: Shadow of Chernobyl. The soundtrack was composed by the Russian electronic band Newtone.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
